title: The Wholefood Store
description: At The Mall on Main Campus, this shop providing prepared hot food as well as many vegetarian and vegan items including a range of grains, dried fruits, nuts, fresh baked bread, fresh produce, and an assortment of groceries. Ingredients are labeled on all the prepared food, and the staff can warm it for you. Convenient for students and staff at Flinders University.
streetAddress: Flinders University, Sturt Road, Bedford Park
